    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "> As for the warning, this is because you're using `DynamicWidgets` which adds the refinement list a bit later so that's why you see this warning. It will not show in code built for production, so you can safely ignore it.\r\n\r\nThat makes sense, thanks for that :)\r\n\r\n",
